<zk xmlns:w="client" xmlns:n="native">

<n:h3>Default well</n:h3>
<n:p>Use the well as a simple effect on an element to give it an inset effect.</n:p>
	<div class="bs-example">
		<div class="well">Look, I'm in a well!</div>
	</div>

	<div class="highlight">
	<n:pre style="white-space:pre;"><![CDATA[<span style='color:#7f0055; '>&lt;</span><span style='color:#7f0055; '>div</span> class=<span style='color:#2a00ff; '>"</span><span style='color:#2a00ff; '>well</span><span style='color:#2a00ff; '>"</span><span style='color:#7f0055; '>></span>Look, I'm in a well!<span style='color:#7f0055; '>&lt;/</span><span style='color:#7f0055; '>div</span><span style='color:#7f0055; '>></span>]]></n:pre>
	</div>	
	
<n:h3>Optional classes</n:h3>
<n:p>Control padding and rounded corners with two optional modifier classes.</n:p>
	<div class="bs-example">
		<div class="well well-lg">Look, I'm in a large well!</div>
	</div>

	<div class="highlight">
	<n:pre style="white-space:pre;"><![CDATA[<span style='color:#7f0055; '>&lt;</span><span style='color:#7f0055; '>div</span> class=<span style='color:#2a00ff; '>"</span><span style='color:#2a00ff; '>well well-lg</span><span style='color:#2a00ff; '>"</span><span style='color:#7f0055; '>></span>Look, I'm in a well!<span style='color:#7f0055; '>&lt;/</span><span style='color:#7f0055; '>div</span><span style='color:#7f0055; '>></span>]]></n:pre>
	</div>
	
	<div class="bs-example">
		<div class="well well-sm">Look, I'm in a large well!</div>
	</div>

	<div class="highlight">
	<n:pre style="white-space:pre;"><![CDATA[<span style='color:#7f0055; '>&lt;</span><span style='color:#7f0055; '>div</span> class=<span style='color:#2a00ff; '>"</span><span style='color:#2a00ff; '>well well-sm</span><span style='color:#2a00ff; '>"</span><span style='color:#7f0055; '>></span>Look, I'm in a well!<span style='color:#7f0055; '>&lt;/</span><span style='color:#7f0055; '>div</span><span style='color:#7f0055; '>></span>]]></n:pre>
	</div>	
</zk>